text: Elfriede Hirnschall (born 16 February 1945) is an Austrian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
